### 5、MySQL服务启动停止

```
//查看状态
systemctl status mysqld
//停止服务
service mysqld stop
//初始化数据库
mysqld --initialize --console
//目录授权
chown -R mysql:mysql /var/lib/mysql/
//启动服务
systemctl start mysqld
systemctl status mysqld
```

